## Qualitative Results

### Domains
Of the 16 BCT domains identified in the BCTTv1, participants in this study used BCTs 14. No responses in the transcripts were attributed to BCTs within the domains of *Scheduled Consequences* or *Covert Learning*. Alternatively, all participants mentioned engaging with techniques within the domains of *Goals and Planning* and *Feedback and Monitoring*.
